title: IBC Integration
description: This batch upload proposal contains all the IBC Integration contracts.

proposals.title: IBC-Core
proposals.description: IBC-Core is the official implementation of the Inter-Blockchain Communication (IBC) protocol, facilitating standardized communication and interoperability among distinct blockchain networks

proposals.title: Icon-light-client
proposals.description: The IBC icon-light-client facilitates trustless communication between blockchain networks by employing cryptographic proofs to verify the validity and correct execution of transactions

proposals.title: xcall
proposals.description: The xCall contract in the IBC protocol serves as a secure gateway, enabling cross-chain communication and token transfers between distinct blockchain networks

proposals.title: xcall-ibc-connection
proposals.description: This contract abstracts the IBC-specific implementation from xCall, serving as a bridge between the IBC host and xCall
